## 6. Project Scope

### In Scope
- Personal Loans
- Home Loans
- Education Loans
- Loan Origination to Disbursement
- Operational & compliance workflows

### Out of Scope
- Loan collections & recovery
- Advanced ML-based credit models (future phase)

---

## 7. AS-IS Process Analysis

### 7.1 Loan Application Intake
- Physical or emailed application forms
- Manual data entry into spreadsheets or legacy systems

**Pain Points**
- Data duplication
- Missing or incorrect information
- Dependency on individual staff members

---

### 7.2 Document Verification
- Physical document handling
- Email-based verification
- Manual checklist tracking

**Issues**
- Lost or outdated documents
- No version control
- Delayed verification cycles

---

### 7.3 Credit Assessment
- Manual credit score retrieval
- Physical income verification
- Underwriter-dependent decisioning

**Risks**
- Subjective approvals
- Inconsistent policy application
- High rework rate

---

### 7.4 Approval & Sanction
- Multi-level approvals via email
- No SLA tracking
- Limited customer visibility

---

### 7.5 Disbursement
- Manual coordination with accounts team
- Delays due to missing approvals
- Weak audit trails

---

## 8. AS-IS Pain Point Summary

| Dimension | Impact |
|---|---|
| Turnaround Time | 10â€“25 days |
| Cost | High operational expenses |
| Risk | Compliance gaps |
| Experience | Low customer satisfaction |
| Scalability | Limited growth capacity |

---

## 9. TO-BE Process Vision

The future-state design focused on a **digitally orchestrated, rule-driven loan processing model**.

### Design Principles
- Single source of truth
- Straight-Through Processing (STP)
- Role-based access & workflows
- Real-time status visibility
- Compliance by design

---

## 10. TO-BE Digital Loan Process

### 10.1 Digital Loan Application
- Web/mobile application
- Guided forms with validations
- Real-time eligibility checks

**Outcome:** Faster and error-free applications

---

### 10.2 Document Upload & Verification
- Centralized document repository
- Automated completeness checks
- Role-based verification queues

---

### 10.3 Credit Decisioning
- Rule-based underwriting engine
- Automated credit bureau integration
- Policy-driven approval thresholds

---

### 10.4 Approval Workflow
- Configurable approval matrix
- SLA tracking & auto-escalations
- Digital sanction letters

---

### 10.5 Disbursement & Communication
- Automated disbursement triggers
- Customer notifications at every stage
- End-to-end digital audit trail

---

## 11. Business Requirements (BRD Highlights)

### Functional Requirements
- Digital loan application module
- Document management system
- Credit rule engine
- Approval workflow management
- Customer status dashboard
- MIS & regulatory reporting

### Non-Functional Requirements
- Data security & encryption
- Scalability & performance SLAs
- Auditability & traceability
- Regulatory compliance

---

