## 13. Sample User Stories

- As a loan applicant, I want to track my loan status online so that I donâ€™t need to visit the branch.
- As a credit officer, I want automated credit score integration to ensure faster and consistent decisions.
- As a compliance officer, I want a complete audit trail to support regulatory reviews.

