## 16. Risk & Compliance Analysis

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Regulatory non-compliance | Policy-driven rule engine |
| Data breaches | Role-based access control |
| Fraud | Automated validation checks |
| Operational dependency | Workflow automation |

