## 20. Key Learnings

- Clear processes must precede automation
- Stakeholder alignment is critical to adoption
- Policy clarity reduces operational risk
- Transparency improves customer trust

---

## 21. Conclusion

This project demonstrates how **structured business analysis and digital transformation** can modernize traditional banking operations into a **scalable, compliant, and customer-centric loan processing system**.

It reflects real-world banking transformation practices and is suitable for:
- Business Analyst portfolios
- Consulting interviews
- Banking / fintech roles
- Training simulations

